Package asap.faceengine.lipsync

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoarticulationLipSyncProvider
    Moves the lips using dominance functions and some coarticulation rules
    CoarticulationLipSyncProviderLoader  
    DominanceFU
    This class implements the dominance function.
    DominanceParameterLoader
    Fills a HashMap with a set of a viseme-number and the corresponding parameters for a dominance function read from a XML-file
    DominanceParameters
    A simple class serving as an extended data type to store all parameters for a dominance function.
    MagnitudeLoader
    Fills a HashMap with a set of a phoneme and the corresponding magnitude-modifiers read from a XML-file.
    SoundClassDifferenceCalculator
    This class sole purpose is to return the numeric difference between two sound-classes to define their disparity.
    SoundClassLoader
    Fills a HashMap with a set of a phoneme and the corresponding sound-class read from a XML-file.
    TimedFaceUnitIncrementalLipSynchProvider
    Provides incremental lipsync using TimedFaceUnits.
    TimedFaceUnitLipSynchProvider
    Creates TimedFaceUnits for lipsync
